6. d3 d6 7. Nd2
{ This is an original plan which I have both faced and employed myself. It is slow and rather inflexible though, so I do not think it leads to much. }
7... Nge7 8. Nf1 a6 9. Ne3 Rb8 10. a4 O-O 11. O-O Nb4
{ or  11...b6!?=  Vigorito - Ashley, Philadelphia 2000. } 12. Bd2
{ Now White may consider a4-a5, so } 12... b6
{ Here Black can easily fight for the d5-square. } *

