{ was played in Uesugi, S-Vigorito,D Washington, 2009. White may hope to play Qb5 to tickle the c5-pawn, but the simple }
12... Rc8
{ overprotects the c6-knight. Black intends ... O-O and ...b6 at an appropriate moment. }
*

