13... Nxd5 14. cxd5 Bxd2+ 15. Qxd2 Nb4
{ White cannot castle kingside, and castling long allows ...Nxa2 } 16. a3 Nxd5
17. exd5 Re8
{ Technically the strongest, but there is also the simple  17...Qxb3  with a winning position. }
18. Nc1 exf4+ 19. Kf1 Bd7 20. Bf3 Bh3+ 21. Bg2
