{ This is untried. White's play looks awkward and he is behind in development, but Black does not have any great way to punish him. }
8... d5 9. cxd5 Nxd5 10. Ncxd5 exd5 11. Bg2 Bxe3 12. Bxe3 d4 13. Bf4
