{ This is the most active and it gains a tempo. Black is under a little pressure after  22...Rxe2  23.Rfc1  Rb6  24.Bg2 }
23. Rc4 Rxe2 24. Rfc1 Nxf2 25. Rxc6+ Kd8
{ This is likely to end in some kind of perpetual check. } *

