9. Nxc6 Qxd1+ 10. Rxd1 bxc6
{ Black's pawns are broken, but he is ready to play ...Nd5. } 11. Bxc4 Nd5 12.
Bg3 { The only ambitious try. } 12... Nxc3 13. bxc3 Bxc3+ 14. Ke2 a5
