19... Kxf7 20. Nd6+ Ke6
{ Instead  20...Kf6  21.Qf3+  Ke6  22.Qd5+  amounts to the same thing. } 21.
Qd5+ Kf6 22. Qf3+ Ke6 { With a draw by repetition. } *

