Qc7 9. Be2 b6 10. O-O Bb7 11. Bg5 Ne5
{ This direct move is a favorite of MVL. Instead 11...h6 is more popular, but considering the bishop usually retreats to h4 anyway, why should we bother? A bunch of rook moves are also playable: 11...Rac8, ...Rfd8, and ...Rad8 for example. }
